import Action from "../Actions";

let initialState = [
	{   'id': '1',
		'name': 'Vlad',
		'description': 'I\'m looking a job right now.',
		'country': 'Ukraine',
		'city': 'Kiev'},
	
	{   'id': '2',
		'name': 'Valera',
		'description': 'I\'m so pretty.',
		'country': 'Belarus',
		'city': 'Minsk'},
	
	{   'id': '3',
		'name': 'Carl',
		'description': 'I found the job.',
		'country': 'France',
		'city': 'Paris'},
	
	{   'id': '4',
		'name': 'Smith',
		'description': 'I\'m free to help you.',
		'country': 'USA',
		'city':  'Los Angeles'},
]

const usersReducer = (state = initialState, action) => {
	switch (action.type) {
		case Action.LOAD_MORE:
			return structuredClone(state)
		
		case Action.LOAD_LESS:
			return structuredClone(state)
		
		default: return structuredClone(state)
	}
}

export default usersReducer;
